<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Heinz to Unveil
   Recyclable Bottle
   For Its Ketchup
   ---
   Squeezable Plastic Container
   Designed to Meet Concern
   On Solid-Waste Disposal
   ----
   By James S. Hirsch
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/09/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B3
</SO>
